rows.name: Byakko! What're you stumbling for?

rows.label: bf07220100_0030
rows.name:
Sorry, my lady. I've been
feeling a little dizzy...

rows.label: bf07220100_0040
rows.name: You too?

rows.label: bf07220100_0050
rows.name: You too, Kagutsuchi-sama?

rows.label: bf07220100_0060
rows.name:
Yes, for a little while now. Though
I'm still capable of standing.

rows.label: bf07220100_0070
rows.name: Me too...

rows.label: bf07220100_0080
rows.name:
What's up with this place?
It's kinda creepy.

rows.label: bf07220100_0090
rows.name: What's going on?

rows.label: bf07220100_0100
rows.name: Just as I thought...

rows.label: bf07220100_0110
rows.name:
Gramps, do you know
something about this?

rows.label: bf07220100_0120
rows.name:
The tales say that Spirit Crucible
Elpys saps the strength of Blades.

rows.label: bf07220100_0130
rows.name:
It's one of the reasons why none
have ever returned from its depths.

rows.label: bf07220100_0140
rows.name: Hmm...

rows.label: bf07220100_0150
rows.name:
The surrounding ether field has become
thin mo. That might be the cause mo.

rows.label: bf07220100_0160
rows.name: Like at the Luxuria palace?

rows.label: bf07220100_0170
rows.name: That's not the only thing, mo.

rows.label: bf07220100_0180
rows.name:
Glowing particles in air... They absorb
ether. That is source of light.

rows.label: bf07220100_0190
rows.name:
So not only can't you gain power, but
you're also having it taken away?

rows.label: bf07220100_0200
rows.name: That's a troublesome situation.

rows.label: bf07220100_0210
rows.name: Hana, are you feeling alright?

rows.label: bf07220100_0220
rows.name: Hana is fine. Hana is very energetic.

rows.label: bf07220100_0230
rows.name:
Of course, you're an
artificial Blade, arent you?
